<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Guarantor Verification Required</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #059669;
            color: white;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #f0fdf4;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #059669;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .button:hover {
            background-color: #047857;
        }
        .details {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #059669;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        .warning {
            background-color: #fef3c7;
            border: 1px solid #f59e0b;
            color: #92400e;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="header">
    <h1>Pax Romana KNUST</h1>
    <h2>Guarantor Verification Required</h2>
</div>

<div class="content">
    <p>Dear {{guarantorName}},</p>

    <p>You have been selected as a guarantor for <strong>{{nomineeName}}</strong> who is contesting for the position of <strong>{{position}}</strong> in the upcoming Pax Romana KNUST elections for the 2025/2026 academic & spiritual year.</p>

    <div class="details">
        <h3>Nomination Details:</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Nominee:</strong> {{nomineeName}}</li>
            <li><strong>Position:</strong> {{position}}</li>
            <li><strong>Submission Date:</strong> {{submissionDate}}</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <p>As a guarantor, you are confirming that you know the nominee personally and believe they are qualified for this position.</p>

    <p>Please click the button below to verify and endorse this nomination:</p>

    <div style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="{{verificationUrl}}" class="button">Verify Endorsement</a>
    </div>

    <div class="warning">
        <strong>⚠️ Important:</strong> This link will expire in {{expirationHours}} hours.
    </div>

    <p>If you did not agree to be a guarantor or if you have any concerns about this nomination, please contact the Electoral Commission immediately.</p>

    <p>Thank you for your participation in the democratic process.</p>

    <p>Best regards,<br>
        Pax Romana KNUST Electoral Commission</p>
</div>

<div class="footer">
    <p>© 2025 Pax Romana KNUST. All rights reserved.</p>
    <p>If you're having trouble clicking the button, copy and paste this URL into your browser: {{verificationUrl}}</p>
</div>
</body>
</html>